./.title: Introduction
./.body:
Introduction
This is a demonstration of a book published using Git Pages and Git Book.
Use the table of contents to navigate to other chapters of this book. Right now I've just put in some filler content!
You may have to open the table of contents if it is currently closed.

Example of Table of Contents Closed. Look for the menu button to open up the table of contents.
 

Example of the table of contents opened. Look for the menu button to close this up, if you want to focus on reading through chapters.
 


You can also customize your personal presentation of the book using the font presentation menu. 
Make sure to check out the Demonstration of what GitBook can support and let me know if you think this would be helpful!
